'''Peter Bernstein''' is a composer for both television and film. The son of composer [[Wikipedia:Elmer Bernstein|Elmer Bernstein]], Peter scored both ''[[Caravan of Courage: An Ewok Adventure]]'' and ''[[Ewoks: The Battle for Endor]]''.

